          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">The price is from the year 2023. The price is estimated as a proxy based on the source: https://pilotpassion.com/how-much-does-a-crop-duster-plane-cost/. The prices were adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2023-06-01).</comment>
        </property>
        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">The production volume has been estimated summing the amount of airplane produced for this specific sources.173 Air Tractor from this source (https://airtractor.com/news/2022/07/air-tractor-aims-for-record-aircraft-production-in-2022/) from 2022 and 27 Ipanema from this source (https://www.militaryaerospace.com/commercial-aerospace/article/14232089/embraer-ipanema-crop-duster) from 2021.</productionVolumeComment>
