        <samplingProcedure xml:lang="en">This dataset was modelled based on "aircraft production, passenger aircraft, very short haul, GLO" and inputs/outputs were scaled down based on the avarage weight of the agricultural aircraft. (avarage 2012 kg).References "Jemioło W., Cox B., Solvoli G., 2015. Life cycle assessment of current and future passenger air transport in Switzerland, Technology Assessment Group, Laboratory for Energy System Analysis Paul Scherrer Institut (PSI), Switzerland, Mater Thesis  Available at. https://www.sccer-mobility.ch/export/sites/sccer-mobility/capacity-areas/dwn_capacity_areas/Jemiolo_Thesis_Final.pdf"                          (Air Tractor, 2022. Agriculture Aircraft, Air Tractor, INC Available at: https://airtractor.com/aircraft/at-402b/; Aviastar, 2022. Embraer EMB-200/201 Ipanema,  Aviastar  Available at: http://www.aviastar.org/air/brazil/embraer_ipanema.php)</samplingProcedure>
